@startuml
title Match Collector State Flow -- Rate Limits, Checkpoints, Seed Expansion, and Queue Filtering

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam wrapWidth 150
skinparam maxMessageSize 70
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor white
  BorderColor black
  FontColor black
  StartColor black
  EndColor black
}

[*] --> Configure

Configure : Select collector config
Configure : Flex, SoloQ, or custom JSON
Configure : Resolve dataset, queue, limits, and seeds

Configure --> CheckpointDecision

state "Checkpoint exists?" as CheckpointDecision <<choice>>
CheckpointDecision --> RestoreRun : yes
CheckpointDecision --> StartFresh : no

RestoreRun : Restore frontier and processed players
RestoreRun : Continue from saved checkpoint

StartFresh : Create initial frontier from seed players
StartFresh : Write first checkpoint

RestoreRun --> Collecting
StartFresh --> Collecting

Collecting : Base collection state
Collecting : Take next player from frontier
Collecting : Fetch match ids and match details
Collecting : Respect Riot API rate limits

Collecting --> ApiDecision

state "API / data result?" as ApiDecision <<choice>>
ApiDecision --> RateLimited : HTTP 429
ApiDecision --> RecoverableError : temporary error or invalid payload
ApiDecision --> QueueFilter : match data received
ApiDecision --> Finish : frontier empty, limit reached, or stop requested

RateLimited : Wait Retry-After or configured delay
RateLimited : Keep current progress
RateLimited --> Collecting

RecoverableError : Log error
RecoverableError : Skip or quarantine invalid item
RecoverableError : Write checkpoint if needed
RecoverableError --> Collecting

QueueFilter : Accept only configured queue
QueueFilter : Flex 440 or SoloQ 420
QueueFilter : Reject duplicate or incomplete matches

QueueFilter --> SaveDecision

state "Match accepted?" as SaveDecision <<choice>>
SaveDecision --> SaveMatch : yes
SaveDecision --> Collecting : no

SaveMatch : Save raw match JSON
SaveMatch : Update player stub
SaveMatch : Write periodic checkpoint

SaveMatch --> ExpandDecision

state "Expand frontier?" as ExpandDecision <<choice>>
ExpandDecision --> ExpandFrontier : yes
ExpandDecision --> Collecting : no

ExpandFrontier : Add newly discovered players
ExpandFrontier : Avoid processed, queued, or invalid PUUIDs
ExpandFrontier : Write checkpoint
ExpandFrontier --> Collecting

Finish : Write final checkpoint
Finish : Write collection metadata
Finish : Dataset ready for normalization and graph building

Finish --> [*]

@enduml
